code: @Override public void readFrom(StreamInput in) throws IOException {     super.readFrom(in).     if (in.readBoolean()) {         license = License.readLicense(in).     } }

@Override public void writeTo(StreamOutput out) throws IOException {     super.writeTo(out).     if (license == null) {         out.writeBoolean(false).     } else {         out.writeBoolean(true).         license.writeTo(out).     } }
